587
00:25:04,680 --> 00:25:05,610
What do you mean?

588
00:25:05,840 --> 00:25:07,240
You just don't want to listen to me!

589
00:25:07,240 --> 00:25:08,640
I can't hear you. I can't hear you.

590
00:25:08,640 --> 00:25:09,570
I can't hear you.

591
00:25:29,720 --> 00:25:31,080
Ziqiu, what brought you here?

592
00:25:31,080 --> 00:25:32,200
Look who is

593
00:25:32,200 --> 00:25:33,130
working so hard.

594
00:25:33,880 --> 00:25:34,920
