596
00:25:35,920 --> 00:25:36,760
Thank you.

597
00:25:37,600 --> 00:25:39,200
Zhou Miao, have some coffee.

598
00:25:39,480 --> 00:25:40,400
I'll pass.

599
00:25:40,400 --> 00:25:42,460
I don't want to go sleepless tonight.

600
00:25:45,840 --> 00:25:47,440
