602
00:25:48,440 --> 00:25:48,960
It's OK.

603
00:25:48,960 --> 00:25:50,520
There're three cups of coffee.

604
00:25:50,520 --> 00:25:51,320
I'll take one.

605
00:25:55,760 --> 00:25:56,440
Thank you.

606
00:25:56,520 --> 00:25:57,160
It's OK.

607
00:26:00,680 --> 00:26:01,480
Ziqiu,

608
00:26:01,480 --> 00:26:03,540
