616
00:26:12,080 --> 00:26:13,240
Can you hurry up?

617
00:26:13,240 --> 00:26:14,240
Don't waste time.

618
00:26:14,280 --> 00:26:16,480
Right away. Wait for me to wash my hands.

619
00:26:26,560 --> 00:26:27,240
Let's go.

620
00:26:27,680 --> 00:26:28,210
Let's go.

621
00:26:28,400 --> 00:26:29,360
See you.

622
00:26:32,120 --> 00:26:32,680
Bye.

623
00:26:32,760 --> 00:26:33,320
Bye.

624
00:26:33,560 --> 00:26:34,680
Ziqiu, drop by when you have time.

625
00:26:34,680 --> 00:26:35,320
Bye.

626
00:26:40,960 --> 00:26:42,520
What's the matter with you?

627
00:26:43,320 --> 00:26:43,980
Look at her.

628
00:26:44,720 --> 00:26:46,650
She acted like nothing is going on.

629
00:26:46,720 --> 00:26:48,640
I feel like I'm worried about her like a fool.

630
00:26:48,640 --> 00:26:49,600
I told you!

631
00:26:49,600 --> 00:26:50,920
Since there is no evidence,

632
00:26:50,920 --> 00:26:52,180
no one will believe us.

633
00:26:52,280 --> 00:26:53,520
I don't believe a picture is

634
00:26:53,520 --> 00:26:54,380
so hard to find.

635
00:26:54,480 --> 00:26:56,140
I don't think it exists at all.

636
00:26:56,400 --> 00:26:58,080
It certainly exists.

637
00:26:58,080 --> 00:26:59,610
Hasn't Li Jianjian said it?

638
00:27:00,200 --> 00:27:01,730
Why do you trust her so much?

639
00:27:03,360 --> 00:27:04,680
What do you mean?

640
00:27:07,880 --> 00:27:08,640
Juan,

641
00:27:09,480 --> 00:27:11,800
you're so naive and innocent.

642
00:27:13,040 --> 00:27:13,920
Haven't you

643
00:27:13,920 --> 00:27:16,120
ever suspected that Miss Li might copy Yufei's work?

644
00:27:16,120 --> 00:27:17,920
No one who did that will admit it?

645
00:27:18,840 --> 00:27:19,920
Look at Yufei.

646
00:27:20,600 --> 00:27:21,480
He's famous

647
00:27:21,480 --> 00:27:22,410
in the industry.

648
00:27:23,040 --> 00:27:24,720
He's talented and has produced many works.

649
00:27:24,720 --> 00:27:26,080
He carried out his own exhibitions.

650
00:27:26,080 --> 00:27:27,880
Does he ever need to plagiarize?

651
00:27:29,200 --> 00:27:30,800
Then what do you really mean?

652
00:27:31,320 --> 00:27:32,840
I've made it so clear.

653
00:27:33,960 --> 00:27:35,960
I find that only you think

654
00:27:35,960 --> 00:27:37,160
Miss Li has talents.

655
00:27:38,360 --> 00:27:39,160
In my opinion,

656
00:27:39,520 --> 00:27:40,920
her works are just so-so.

657
00:27:41,160 --> 00:27:42,320
She's a craftsman

658
00:27:42,320 --> 00:27:43,080
at best,

659
00:27:43,440 --> 00:27:45,440
far from being an artist.

660
00:27:46,240 --> 00:27:47,640
Yufei is different.

661
00:27:47,840 --> 00:27:49,440
He often deals with artists.

662
00:27:49,520 --> 00:27:50,880
He lived in Paris,

663
00:27:50,880 --> 00:27:52,810
the center of arts, for a long time.

664
00:27:53,560 --> 00:27:54,400
I don't think

665
00:27:54,600 --> 00:27:56,260
she can produce any evidence.

666
00:27:56,600 --> 00:27:57,760
She signed a contract

667
00:27:57,760 --> 00:27:59,000
with the furniture factory,

668
00:27:59,000 --> 00:28:00,560
which carries explicit terms.

669
00:28:00,560 --> 00:28:02,760
Whoever violates it must pay a penalty.

670
00:28:02,880 --> 00:28:03,740
Are you going to

671
00:28:04,000 --> 00:28:05,860
share the hefty penalty with her?

672
00:28:07,880 --> 00:28:09,080
Are you stupid?

673
00:28:09,280 --> 00:28:11,140
What does this have to do with you?

674
00:28:11,400 --> 00:28:13,240
You two started the studio together.

675
00:28:13,240 --> 00:28:15,600
You deserve to get the return on investment.

676
00:28:15,600 --> 00:28:17,800
The plagiarism is just her own problem.

677
00:28:18,880 --> 00:28:19,600
Besides,

678
00:28:19,880 --> 00:28:22,010
we're also victims of her plagiarism.

679
00:28:22,200 --> 00:28:24,880
We're kind enough not to make her pay for our loss.

680
00:28:24,880 --> 00:28:27,280
Then what are you really trying to say?

681
00:28:29,600 --> 00:28:31,200
My silly girl!

682
00:28:33,040 --> 00:28:34,160
What I'm saying is that

683
00:28:34,160 --> 00:28:35,840
since she signed the contract

684
00:28:36,040 --> 00:28:37,300
with only her own name,

685
00:28:37,360 --> 00:28:38,360
if you stop working with her,

686
00:28:38,360 --> 00:28:40,360
you don't need to share the penalty.

687
00:28:40,600 --> 00:28:41,600
Why must you share

688
00:28:41,600 --> 00:28:42,480
the penalty?

689
00:28:43,000 --> 00:28:44,120
Stop working with her?

690
00:28:44,120 --> 00:28:44,680
Yeah.

691
00:28:45,760 --> 00:28:46,890
You can work with me.

692
00:28:46,960 --> 00:28:48,420
I will graduate next year.

693
00:28:57,120 --> 00:28:57,840
Juan,

694
00:28:58,640 --> 00:29:00,170
I know you're kindhearted.

695
00:29:00,760 --> 00:29:01,820
But think about it.

696
00:29:02,040 --> 00:29:03,360
I won't hurt you.

697
00:29:03,480 --> 00:29:05,280
