699
00:29:07,160 --> 00:29:07,820
Seriously!

700
00:29:08,280 --> 00:29:09,560
I wish I could take my heart out

701
00:29:09,560 --> 00:29:10,320
to show you.

702
00:29:11,000 --> 00:29:12,600
Alright, stop talking.

703
00:29:14,560 --> 00:29:15,120
Fine.

704
00:29:16,400 --> 00:29:17,200
How about

705
00:29:17,400 --> 00:29:19,280
I take you to a good restaurant in the evening?

706
00:29:19,280 --> 00:29:20,340
I have no appetite.

707
00:29:20,840 --> 00:29:21,700
I'm going home.

708
00:29:23,520 --> 00:29:24,160
OK.

709
00:29:24,720 --> 00:29:26,520
Think about it when you get home.

710
00:29:27,200 --> 00:29:28,000
Wait a minute.

711
00:29:29,360 --> 00:29:30,200
Your apron.

712
00:29:33,720 --> 00:29:34,600
Let me take you home.

713
00:29:34,600 --> 00:29:35,400
No, thanks.

714
00:29:51,280 --> 00:29:52,520
Did Mr. Ling

715
00:29:53,000 --> 00:29:54,280
make tea like this?

716
00:29:54,600 --> 00:29:54,840
He poured water...

717
00:29:54,840 --> 00:29:56,680
Just pour it in. And it'll be done.

718
00:29:56,680 --> 00:29:58,280
Yes. I can do it anyway I like.

719
00:29:58,520 --> 00:29:59,250
Let's drink.

720
00:30:01,320 --> 00:30:02,800
Have some sunflower seeds.

721
00:30:02,800 --> 00:30:04,120
Thank you, Ms. Zhu.

722
00:30:05,520 --> 00:30:06,200
Ziqiu,

723
00:30:07,160 --> 00:30:08,520
what is going on

724
00:30:08,520 --> 00:30:10,640
between Mr. Li and your mother at the moment?

725
00:30:10,640 --> 00:30:11,570
What do you mean?

726
00:30:11,600 --> 00:30:13,120
The other day while you were not here,

727
00:30:13,120 --> 00:30:14,380
there was quite a show.

728
00:30:14,640 --> 00:30:15,920
Your mother came to visit Mr. Li

729
00:30:15,920 --> 00:30:16,920
and asked him to teach her

730
00:30:16,920 --> 00:30:18,780
how to cook your favorite dishes.

731
00:30:19,600 --> 00:30:20,640
But

732
00:30:20,920 --> 00:30:22,400
they bumped into Mrs. Qian and Ms. Zhang

733
00:30:22,400 --> 00:30:23,600
