734
00:30:23,600 --> 00:30:24,480
Hasn't my father broken up

735
00:30:24,480 --> 00:30:25,340
with Ms. Zhang?

736
00:30:25,440 --> 00:30:26,520
Broken up?

737
00:30:26,760 --> 00:30:28,420
They haven't even held hands.

738
00:30:28,880 --> 00:30:29,840
But Ms. Zhang acted

739
00:30:29,840 --> 00:30:30,840
quite enviously.

740
00:30:31,200 --> 00:30:32,680
She said she liked Mr. Li for his kindness,

741
00:30:32,680 --> 00:30:34,560
but that Mr. Li only liked beautiful women.

742
00:30:34,560 --> 00:30:36,600
Mr. Li got very embarrassed.

743
00:30:37,160 --> 00:30:37,890
At this time,

744
00:30:38,040 --> 00:30:39,770
your mother stood out and said,

745
00:30:39,880 --> 00:30:41,160
"You like his kindness,

746
00:30:41,160 --> 00:30:42,440
he likes my look.

747
00:30:42,440 --> 00:30:44,240
No one is better than the other."

748
00:30:45,080 --> 00:30:46,880
Ms. He Mei was so amazing.

749
00:30:46,880 --> 00:30:48,240
I heard today that

750
00:30:48,240 --> 00:30:49,120
Mr. Li asked your mother

751
00:30:49,120 --> 00:30:50,720
to go to a bookshop tomorrow.

752
00:30:51,040 --> 00:30:52,700
They started dating already?

753
00:30:52,920 --> 00:30:54,280
