765
00:31:15,040 --> 00:31:15,800
OK, I got it, dad.

766
00:31:15,800 --> 00:31:18,000
Please carry on with what you're doing.

767
00:31:20,080 --> 00:31:21,200
What are you

768
00:31:21,200 --> 00:31:22,600
up to?

769
00:31:22,600 --> 00:31:23,480
Nothing.

770
00:31:23,680 --> 00:31:24,440
Don't worry about us.

771
00:31:24,440 --> 00:31:25,520
We'll go home soon.

772
00:31:25,960 --> 00:31:26,480
Dad.

773
00:31:37,960 --> 00:31:38,800
Ziqiu!

774
00:31:39,040 --> 00:31:39,680
What?

775
00:31:40,280 --> 00:31:41,240
If my father and Ms. He Mei

776
00:31:41,240 --> 00:31:42,280
get married,

777
00:31:42,280 --> 00:31:42,960
all our names will be

778
00:31:42,960 --> 00:31:44,760
on the same household register.

779
00:31:47,160 --> 00:31:47,800
What?

780
00:31:48,080 --> 00:31:49,740
You don't want that to happen?

781
00:31:49,960 --> 00:31:51,560
