No.

791
00:32:10,000 --> 00:32:10,720
Say yes, please.

792
00:32:10,720 --> 00:32:11,480
No.

793
00:32:11,640 --> 00:32:13,120
Ziqiu!

794
00:32:13,360 --> 00:32:14,620
When I say no, I mean no.

795
00:32:14,840 --> 00:32:15,920
Ziqiu!

796
00:32:16,120 --> 00:32:17,400
I mean it.

797
00:32:17,400 --> 00:32:18,200
I'm not your boyfriend.

798
00:32:18,200 --> 00:32:19,040
