799
00:32:19,040 --> 00:32:19,840
It won't work.

800
00:32:20,280 --> 00:32:20,840
You're a bummer.

801
00:32:20,840 --> 00:32:22,370
I'll do it myself tomorrow.

802
00:32:22,440 --> 00:32:23,600
Don't do that!

803
00:32:23,600 --> 00:32:26,720
If you don't want to leave, then help wash the tableware in the kitchen.

804
00:32:26,720 --> 00:32:28,400
Dad, see you.

805
00:32:28,760 --> 00:32:29,960
Let's get out of here.

806
00:32:30,160 --> 00:32:30,800
Dad, see you.

807
00:32:30,800 --> 00:32:31,860
See you later, dad.

808
00:32:39,480 --> 00:32:40,940
Which table ordered this?

809
00:32:49,320 --> 00:32:49,920
Ling Xiao,

810
00:32:50,440 --> 00:32:52,440
