813
00:32:58,280 --> 00:32:59,810
I don't think she needed it.

814
00:33:00,040 --> 00:33:01,040
I don't know much.

815
00:33:01,360 --> 00:33:02,720
Don't talk about it at dinner.

816
00:33:02,720 --> 00:33:04,650
Mr. Ling, have a piece of spare rib.

817
00:33:10,680 --> 00:33:11,560
Jianjian,

818
00:33:12,560 --> 00:33:14,560
you have no news

819
00:33:14,880 --> 00:33:16,480
