824
00:33:24,520 --> 00:33:25,280
Boring?

825
00:33:26,360 --> 00:33:27,640
Ziqiu, what about you?

826
00:33:27,880 --> 00:33:28,720
Me, either.

827
00:33:31,000 --> 00:33:32,130
Is your business OK?

828
00:33:32,160 --> 00:33:32,890
Pretty good.

829
00:33:33,000 --> 00:33:34,000
It's profitable.

830
00:33:35,120 --> 00:33:35,980
What about you?

831
00:33:36,760 --> 00:33:38,040
What are you doing tomorrow?

832
00:33:38,040 --> 00:33:38,560
Me?

833
00:33:39,160 --> 00:33:40,760
It's just business as usual.

834
00:33:41,440 --> 00:33:42,960
I'll go to the restaurant,

835
00:33:43,280 --> 00:33:44,040
and then

836
00:33:44,440 --> 00:33:45,320
I'll go

837
00:33:45,440 --> 00:33:47,240
grocery shopping in the market.

838
00:34:01,920 --> 00:34:02,960
What are you up to?

839
00:34:04,160 --> 00:34:04,960
