843
00:34:12,190 --> 00:34:13,520
What if it is good?

844
00:34:15,000 --> 00:34:15,840
Secret?

845
00:34:16,320 --> 00:34:17,840
Whenever you guys are together, you're always up to no good!

846
00:34:17,840 --> 00:34:18,880
Secret?

847
00:34:19,150 --> 00:34:20,280
Don't make trouble.

848
00:34:24,360 --> 00:34:26,000
I've talked with the director.

849
00:34:26,000 --> 00:34:26,710
I'll memorize my lines

850
00:34:26,710 --> 00:34:27,960
in advance,

851
00:34:27,960 --> 00:34:29,760
and then I'll quit my current job.

852
00:34:29,760 --> 00:34:30,670
You don't have to

853
00:34:30,670 --> 00:34:31,960
pick me up at the theater.

854
00:34:31,960 --> 00:34:33,600
