855
00:34:33,600 --> 00:34:35,280
It's very convenient for me to take a taxi here.

856
00:34:35,280 --> 00:34:37,040
It's OK. I can pick you up along my way home.

857
00:34:37,040 --> 00:34:39,230
Come on. Along your way home?

858
00:34:41,960 --> 00:34:42,710
Are you having a crush

859
00:34:42,710 --> 00:34:43,840
